description: A souvenir of a delightful afternoon conversation with my favorite Jazz Eminence, Mister Morgenstern, at Dan's apartment -- not only musical commentary but first-person encounters with Sonny.  Recorded on July 6, 2018, by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
